<p><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.renewamerica.com%2Fcolumns%2Fmwest%2F131112&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFs7XKoD2Vv-Ymta0wZ9xijsSxvzA" target="_blank">Rick Warren&#8217;s new book &#8220;Daniel Plan: 40 Days to a Healthier Life&#8221; awash with doctrines of demons</a> by Marsha West</p>
<p><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fapprising.org%2F2011%2F11%2F08%2Frick-warren-and-teachings-of-demons%2F&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFujGjTZAYyzm-ufbRjR9pfT3DPcg" target="_blank">Rick Warren and Teaching of Demons</a> by Ken Silva</p>
