<p><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fstandupforthetruth.com%2F2014%2F02%2Fquestions-ask-watching-son-god%2F&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGeqOuvoCv9EJ8JPvrKDVb2RRnSNw" target="_blank">Questions to ask watching the Son of God</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-highway.com%2FHorton_cath.html&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGD0HD9JfITPhvzPPM3RXBt4_QvCA" target="_blank">What Still Keeps Us Apart?</a> by Michael Horton</p>
